<fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/us/">Trending in the United States</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 19:55:43 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 19:55:43 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/07/georgia-teen-school-shooting-suspect-lived-series-rental-homes-emerging-details-shed-light-family.webp" alt="Georgia teen school shooting suspect lived in series of rental homes as emerging details shed light on family" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Georgia teen school shooting suspect lived in series of rental homes as emerging details shed light on family</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Colt Gray, the teen suspect charged in the Apalachee High School shooting, came from a broken home, with the teen living in at least three rental homes in a short period.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/07/georgia-teen-school-shooting-suspect-lived-series-rental-homes-emerging-details-shed-light-family/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 06 Sep 2024 23:43:48 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 06 Sep 2024 23:43:48 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Ryan Nadeau, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/06/photos-oven-destroyed-after-person-puts-loaded-gun-inside-turns-it-on.webp" alt="PHOTOS: Oven destroyed after person puts loaded gun inside, turns it on" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">PHOTOS: Oven destroyed after person puts loaded gun inside, turns it on</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      An oven in a Chesterfield County home was destroyed Thursday night after fire officials say a resident put a loaded gun inside and turned it on, causing the gun to fire off multiple shots.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/06/photos-oven-destroyed-after-person-puts-loaded-gun-inside-turns-it-on/"  >(Ryan Nadeau, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 21:47:16 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 21:47:16 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="David Charns, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/07/las-vegas-police-arrest-pastor-with-guns-drugs-in-hotel-room-sources.webp" alt="Las Vegas police arrest pastor with guns, drugs in hotel room: sources" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Las Vegas police arrest pastor with guns, drugs in hotel room: sources</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Las Vegas Metro police arrested an evangelical pastor for allegedly having guns and drugs in a hotel room in an incident that initially sparked a counter-terrorism response, the 8 News Now Investigators have learned.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/07/las-vegas-police-arrest-pastor-with-guns-drugs-in-hotel-room-sources/"  >(David Charns, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 13:37:17 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 13:37:17 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, KLAS, CBS News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/07/mega-millions-jackpot-soars-to-an-estimated-800-million.webp" alt="Mega Millions jackpot soars to an estimated $800 million" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Mega Millions jackpot soars to an estimated $800 million</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      BOSTON (AP) — The Mega Millions jackpot has risen to an estimated $800 million with a cash option of $401.8 million for Tuesday’s drawing after no one matched all the winning numbers for Friday night's drawing. The jackpot was last won in Illinois on June 4 with a ticket valued at $552 million.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/07/mega-millions-jackpot-soars-to-an-estimated-800-million/"  >(Associated Press, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 20:51:04 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 20:51:04 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Rob Nesbitt, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/07/man-mauled-to-death-by-dogs-in-california-1-arrested.webp" alt="Man mauled to death by dogs in California, 1 arrested" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Man mauled to death by dogs in California, 1 arrested</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      When officers arrived at the scene, they found the victim suffering from several dog bites, police said.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/07/man-mauled-to-death-by-dogs-in-california-1-arrested/"  >(Rob Nesbitt, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 18:56:20 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 18:56:20 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/07/rare-copy-of-us-constitution-went-missing-for-centuries-now-its-being-auctioned-for-millions.webp" alt="Rare copy of US Constitution went missing for centuries. Now it's being auctioned for millions" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Rare copy of US Constitution went missing for centuries. Now it's being auctioned for millions</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      At the top of the first page are familiar words but in regular type instead of the sweeping Gothic script we're used to seeing: “WE, the People "
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/07/rare-copy-of-us-constitution-went-missing-for-centuries-now-its-being-auctioned-for-millions/"  >(The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 12:17:47 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 12:17:47 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="MORIAH BALINGIT, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/07/how-to-pick-the-best-preschool-or-child-care-center-for-your-child.webp" alt="How to pick the best preschool or child care center for your child" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">How to pick the best preschool or child care center for your child</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Preschool options are growing with the expansion of early learning programs, giving families in some parts of the U.S. a dizzying array of choices. Some states, like Colorado and New Mexico, are funneling state money into existing private preschools or child care centers.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/07/how-to-pick-the-best-preschool-or-child-care-center-for-your-child/"  >(MORIAH BALINGIT, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/world/">Around the world</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:16:24 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:16:24 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="KATIE TAM and KANIS LEUNG, Associated Press, PIX 11">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/09/08/villagers-reluctant-to-say-goodbye-to-one-of-hong-kongs-last-squatter-settlements.webp" alt="Villagers reluctant to say goodbye to one of Hong Kong's last squatter settlements" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Villagers reluctant to say goodbye to one of Hong Kong's last squatter settlements</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      HONG KONG (AP) — In months, Lo Yuet-ping will bid farewell to a centuries-old village he has called home in Hong Kong for more than seven decades.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/08/villagers-reluctant-to-say-goodbye-to-one-of-hong-kongs-last-squatter-settlements/"  >(KATIE TAM and KANIS LEUNG, Associated Press, PIX 11)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 03 Sep 2024 02:47:25 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 03 Sep 2024 02:47:25 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="KIM TONG-HYUNG, Associated Press, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/09/03/north-korea-shows-new-drone-attacking-a-target-as-seoul-and-us-hold-large-military-exercises.webp" alt="North Korea shows new drone attacking a target as Seoul and US hold large military exercises" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">North Korea shows new drone attacking a target as Seoul and US hold large military exercises</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SEOUL, South Korea (AP) — North Korean leader Kim Jong Un supervised a demonstration of new exploding drones designed to crash into targets, state media said Monday, as the U.S. and South Korea engage in joint military drills.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/03/north-korea-shows-new-drone-attacking-a-target-as-seoul-and-us-hold-large-military-exercises/"  >(KIM TONG-HYUNG, Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 06:16:30 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 06:16:30 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="JALAL BWAITEL and JULIA FRANKEL, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/09/08/chased-away-by-israeli-settlers-these-palestinians-returned-to-a-village-in-ruins.webp" alt="Chased away by Israeli settlers, these Palestinians returned to a village in ruins" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Chased away by Israeli settlers, these Palestinians returned to a village in ruins</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      KHIRBET ZANUTA, West Bank (AP) — An entire Palestinian community fled their tiny West Bank village last fall after repeated threats from Israeli settlers with a history of violence.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/08/chased-away-by-israeli-settlers-these-palestinians-returned-to-a-village-in-ruins/"  >(JALAL BWAITEL and JULIA FRANKEL, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 18:43:25 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 18:43:25 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Aamer Madhani And Zeke Miller, Associated Press, Local 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/09/07/us-believes-iran-has-transferred-short-range-ballistic-missiles-to-russia-ap-sources-say.webp" alt="US believes Iran has transferred short-range ballistic missiles to Russia, AP sources say" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">US believes Iran has transferred short-range ballistic missiles to Russia, AP sources say</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The United States has informed allies that it believes Iran has transferred short-range ballistic missiles to Russia for its war in Ukraine.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/07/us-believes-iran-has-transferred-short-range-ballistic-missiles-to-russia-ap-sources-say/"  >(Aamer Madhani And Zeke Miller, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 04 Sep 2024 15:30:52 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 04 Sep 2024 15:30:52 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="MARK CARLSON, NICOLAS GARRIGA and JOHN LEICESTER, Associated Press, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/09/04/migrant-boat-seen-trying-to-make-an-apparent-crossing-of-english-channel-a-day-after-12-people-died.webp" alt="A day after 12 deaths, other migrants risk their lives trying to cross the English Channel" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">A day after 12 deaths, other migrants risk their lives trying to cross the English Channel</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      That migrants were prepared to risk their lives so soon after a dozen others lost theirs trying to cross the busy waterway.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/04/migrant-boat-seen-trying-to-make-an-apparent-crossing-of-english-channel-a-day-after-12-people-died/"  >(MARK CARLSON, NICOLAS GARRIGA and JOHN LEICESTER, Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 21:44:57 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 21:44:57 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="ELÉONORE HUGHES and GABRIELA SÁ PESSOA, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/09/07/brazils-x-ban-drives-outraged-bolsonaro-supporters-to-rally-for-free-speech.webp" alt="Brazil's X ban drives outraged Bolsonaro supporters to rally for 'free speech'" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Brazil's X ban drives outraged Bolsonaro supporters to rally for 'free speech'</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SAO PAULO (AP) — Thousands of supporters of former Brazilian President Jair Bolsonaro flooded Sao Paulo’s main boulevard for an Independence Day rally Saturday, buoyed by the government's blocking of tech billionaire Elon Musk's X platform, a ban they say is proof of their political persecution.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/07/brazils-x-ban-drives-outraged-bolsonaro-supporters-to-rally-for-free-speech/"  >(ELÉONORE HUGHES and GABRIELA SÁ PESSOA, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 13:31:58 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 13:31:58 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/09/05/netanyahu-dismisses-claims-imminent-cease-fire-deal-fox-friends-appearance.webp" alt="Netanyahu dismisses claims of imminent cease-fire deal during 'Fox &#38; Friends' appearance" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Netanyahu dismisses claims of imminent cease-fire deal during 'Fox &#38; Friends' appearance</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu this week has repeatedly addressed the press to explain his insistence on keeping control of the Philadelphi Corridor in any cease-fire deal.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/05/netanyahu-dismisses-claims-imminent-cease-fire-deal-fox-friends-appearance/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
