    <h3 itemprop="headline">Ask the CIO: Marine Corps Forces Cyberspace Command</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      How is the Marine Corps Forces Cyberspace Command securing data?
The post Ask the CIO: Marine Corps Forces Cyberspace Command first appeared on Federal News Network.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/09/05/ask-the-cio-marine-corps-forces-cyberspace-command/"  >(wfedstaff, Federal News Network)</a>
