        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">OpenAI might use Apple&#8217;s TSMC for chips</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      In another interesting move that hints at a symbiotic relationship, ChatGPT maker OpenAI has reportedly followed Apple to become a lead customer for TSMC processors.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/09/03/openai-might-use-apples-tsmc-for-chips/"  >(Computer World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
