        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">US widens indictment of Russians in 'WhisperGate' conspiracy to destroy Ukrainian and NATO systems</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      BALTIMORE (AP) — The U.S. Justice Department has widened its indictment of Russians in the so-called WhisperGate malware attacks aimed at destroying computer systems in Ukraine and 26 NATO allies including the United States.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/09/05/us-widens-indictment-of-russians-in-whispergate-conspiracy-to-destroy-ukrainian-and-nato-systems/"  >(BRIAN WITTE, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 00:30:00 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 00:30:00 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Peter Smart, Fast Company">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
