        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Say goodbye to static user interfaces</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      What if the apps and websites you use every day adapted to your needs in real time? If they instantly generated the exact content and functions you need, when you need them?
You’ve heard of generative images and generative videos.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/09/07/say-goodbye-to-static-user-interfaces/"  >(Peter Smart, Fast Company)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT">
