        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Packages and static imports in Java</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      In a previous Java 101 tutorial, you learned how to better organize your code by declaring reference types (also known as classes and interfaces) as members of other reference types and blocks.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/09/05/packages-and-static-imports-in-java/"  >(Info World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
