    <p itemprop="text">
      DENVER (AP) — Denver Nuggets star point guard Jamal Murray has agreed to a four-year, $208 million maximum contract extension, a person with knowledge of the deal told The Associated Press on Saturday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/09/07/nuggets-star-jamal-murray-agrees-to-a-4-year-208m-max-contract-extension-ap-source-says/"  >(ARNIE STAPLETON, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
