        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Footage of motorcade racing JFK to the hospital after he was shot is set to go to auction</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      DALLAS (AP) — Newly emerged film footage of President John F. Kennedy's motorcade speeding down a Dallas freeway toward a hospital after he was fatally wounded will go up for auction later this month. Experts say the find isn't necessarily surprising even over 60 years after the assassination.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/09/05/footage-of-motorcade-racing-jfk-to-the-hospital-after-he-was-shot-is-set-to-go-to-auction/"  >(JAMIE STENGLE, Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
