    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump lawyers, special counsel fight over election interference case in court</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      In a hearing marked by moments of tension and humor, Trump and Justice Department lawyers clashed over how the federal election interference case against the former president should proceed.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/09/05/npr-trump-special-counsel-election-interference/"  >(Carrie Johnson, MPR News)</a>
