    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump claims no 'lifts' or 'stands' will be allowed at debate with Kamala Harris</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Former President Donald Trump claimed on Saturday that boxes or other stands used to increase one&apos;s height behind the podium will not be allowed in his presidential debate against Vice President Kamala Harris.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/09/07/trump-claims-no-lifts-stands-allowed-debate-kamala-harris/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
